H3 Laboratories has some members who are programmers. H3 Laboratories is located in the same building as Glassbox where Texas Ave turns into Alameda Ave. Also there is a Computer Programmer Meetup that meets most days at 7:00 pm at the Starbucks on Mesa near UTEP.
I look forward to meet coders from Southern New Mexico and West Texas.
